{"tid":1249684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外国势力渗入香港警察，难怪容许暴徒破坏社会安宁","createTime":"2019-06-21T19:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T19:18:00.000Z","uid":259462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06a77d743ed177d24f462e87b53c58e0915e17d6","tid":1249684,"uid":259462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:18:00.000Z","msg":"有传香港警队正接受外藉指挥官指示，一方面私通与美国川普政府，藉此打击我国於国际间的地位。另一方面假装镇压暴徒，实际上包庇暴徒的违法行为，使暴动至今仍未平息。我国将严正要求香港政府将所有外藉警司撤职，并且大力严惩有关决策的官员，恢复香港社会和谐安宁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsiOP1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsiOP1N.jpg&h=c7b43057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hiuuztc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiuuztc.jpg&h=8fe4a52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxaNk8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxaNk8w.jpg&h=0b752111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}